{
    "problem": "Compute $\\tan 22.5^\\circ.$",
    "level": "Level 2",
    "type": "Precalculus",
    "solution": "By the half-angle formula,\n\\[\\tan 22.5^\\circ = \\tan \\frac{45^\\circ}{2} = \\frac{1 - \\cos 45^\\circ}{\\sin 45^\\circ} = \\frac{1 - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}}{\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}} = \\boxed{\\sqrt{2} - 1}.\\]"
}